Fellesforbundet Helgeland avd. 143 (the "Client") holds a
non-exclusive, non-transferable right to have the Work operated and
displayed as the Client's website for the duration of the agreement
with the Owner. This does NOT transfer ownership of the source code.

The Client may edit the website's content — text, images and prices —
without consent. This covers content only, not the source code,
design, structure or technical functionality. All other changes
(code, design, functionality, operations, integrations, etc.) must go
through the Owner (T-Event). The domain is owned by the Client
(Fellesforbundet Helgeland) and is not covered by this restriction.

You may NOT, without the Owner's prior written consent: copy,
distribute or publish the source code; modify or create derivative
works of the code, design or technical structure (content editing as
above excepted); transfer, sell, sub-license or lease the Work; let
another vendor operate or continue the Work; or remove copyright
notices.

Ownership of the source code, or any extended right to use or continue
it, can only be acquired through a separate written agreement
(purchase/assignment) with the Owner.

The Work is provided "AS IS", without warranty of any kind, to the
extent permitted by applicable law. Governed by Norwegian law.

